commits.content:
@font-face{font-family:OpenSans-Regular;src:url(../fonts/OpenSans/OpenSans-Regular.ttf)}*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}body,html{height:100%;font-family:sans-serif}a{margin:0;transition:all
.4s;-webkit-transition:all .4s;-o-transition:all .4s;-moz-transition:all
